Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.76,0:58:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,is entitled Composing and\N Decomposing Op-Based CRDTs
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.52,0:58:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,with Semidirect Products.
